{"tid":858850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【不動嶼山】多個團體周日上街反填海 促先收回高球場官地建屋","createTime":"2018-10-12T05:51:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-14T10:18:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"851e88a6f3a0d596f46efaaba9308c522a7102c9","tid":858850,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T05:51:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181012/58786057\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181012%2F58786057&d=WS%2FYp3ECWde12OldG2sREW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=663d78a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181012%2F58786057&h=017e3b58\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181012/58786057</a><br />\n<br />\n【不動嶼山】多個團體周日上街反填海 促先收回高球場官地建屋<br />\n<br />\n51分鐘前<br />\n即時要聞<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181012/large/1539319433_0982.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181012%2Flarge%2F1539319433_0982.png&h=d6f519b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n土地公義聯合陣線和守護大嶼聯盟周日（14日）發起遊行反對「明日大嶼」的1,700公頃填海計劃。馬泉崇攝(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181012/large/1539319433_85ba.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181012%2Flarge%2F1539319433_85ba.png&h=4adf27be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n團體要求政府應率先利用閒置官地、高球場、市區重建等方法增建房屋。馬泉崇攝(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181012/large/1539319433_2777.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181012%2Flarge%2F1539319433_2777.png&h=0709517f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬泉崇攝(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥在《施政報告》公布造價數千億的東大嶼大型填海計劃，引起民間強烈反響，土地公義聯合陣線和守護大嶼聯盟周日（14日）將發起遊行，反對填海造地方案，要求政府先利用閒置官地、高球場、市區重建等方法建公營房屋及院舍。<br />\n<br />\n遊行將於周日（14日）下午3時於銅鑼灣東角道集合和默站，3時半出發遊行前往政府總部，下午6時半於政府總部外有論壇，邀請曾任中文大學地理及資源管理學系副教授的姚松炎等專家分享。<br />\n<br />\n守護大嶼山聯盟召集人謝世傑表示，暫時難以估計遊行人數，期望主辦遊行能搭建平台，讓香港市民表達對計劃的不滿，「集結力量，向林鄭月娥說不」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多個基督宗教團體亦將於遊行前舉行祈禱會，天主教正義和平委員會幹事葉寶琳表示，填海計劃對環境和生態有重大影響，他們相信發展亦不應違反自然規律，故此聯同多個團體在周日下午3時，於銅鑼灣港鐵站D出口對開舉辦祈禱會，呼籲基督徒和天主教徒出席。"},{"pid":"23215ada34e73b033d2a5427dc7d111a74664a8e","tid":858850,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T05:52:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a480bb874f27c1d762ca563d69c8715cc2771980","tid":858850,"uid":5150,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T05:59:32.000Z","msg":"不動嶼山<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邊個諗架個名"},{"pid":"5830e800bfc380c9d470271e4d627ebce97481bf","tid":858850,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T06:00:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d703de97af33968432f591f58969b095bf34c08b","tid":858850,"uid":44562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T06:02:26.000Z","msg":"連登無代表 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aa2b74f3bdeed7ac8d8b403ed510e4fe4150a6a","tid":858850,"uid":171192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T08:15:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9883009f77f09bb67eb7559660c9a6d1ed23603b","tid":858850,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a480bb874f27c1d762ca563d69c8715cc2771980","tid":858850,"uid":5150,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T05:59:32.000Z","msg":"不動嶼山<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邊個諗架個名"},"citedBy":